@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_bislfp(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (v1 + ((v0 + 0.50 + tmp + 0.48) / (v1 + 0.53 * v1 + 0.69)))
    tmp = 0.99
    v2 = ((wp.cos(v1 + 0.18) / (tmp + 0.17 * v1 + 0.14)) / ((tmp + 0.69 * v1 + 0.02) + wp.abs(v0 + 0.20)))
    v2 = wp.abs(tmp)
    v2 = v2
    tmp = v2
    data[tid] = v0
